data.description: Stunning 3 bed, 2 bath home with modern updates! Newer windows illuminate the space, showcasing an updated kitchen with granite counters, stainless appliances, and sleek tile floors. Enjoy gleaming hardwood in the living and dining areas, leading to a deck overlooking a spacious fenced backyard with a storage shed and fire pit. The updated full bathroom boasts granite counters and elegant tile details. The lower level is a retreat with a family room, 3/4 bath, and an additional bedroom, all leading to a patio. Welcome to your new haven!
